snippet.title: Best VGM 2157 - Phantasy Star Online Episode III - Hi, Guys! (Lobby ~ Light)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameCube
Phantasy Star Online Episode III: C.A.R.D. Revolution (2003)

Kenichi Tokoi
